 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-harlow">Jack Harlow</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">Kendrick Lamar</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">Teddy游泳</a>之间。</p><p> K-Pop Group <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">Blackpink</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">Olivia Rodrigo</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">Lisa</a>获得了四个提名，例如游泳，而Boone， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">Anitta</a> ，Tyla，Tyla， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glorilla">Glorilla</a>都在三个中。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a> ＆ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">Shakira</a>和Rauw Alejandro之类的人加入了Anitta和Bad Bunny，是最好的拉丁类别，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a>是最好的嘻哈提名人之一。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-jovi">Bon Jovi</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lenny-kravitz">Lenny Kravitz</a>都被提名为最佳摇滚，而Hozier和Linkin Park是最佳选择。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mtv-vmas-postponed-due-to-trump-vs-harris-debate-3783163">由于特朗普与哈里斯辩论，MTV VMA邮报推迟</a>了首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
