d out of Metallica</a> . Following the allegations against Ellefson, Mustaine came out to say <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeths-dave-mustaine-says-hell-forgive-david-ellefson-but-just-wont-play-music-with-him-anymore-3257121">he&#39;ll “forgive” him, but “just won&#39;t play music with him anymore”</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megadeth-perform-rarity-liar-for-first-time-since-2006-3783149">Megadeth perform rarity &#39;Liar&#39; for first time since 2006</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
